author: Channel Awesome
description:
Doug has surprisingly never talked about a Jackie Chan movie before. Well what better way to start than with his intro film to him?

Watch all DisneyCember here - https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL0AQIMR-tpomecW19RN2LNrdoqd5wFu4R

Watch the new NC - https://youtu.be/iGMHcasHpUg

Rumble in the Bronx is a 1995 Hong Kong action comedy film directed by Stanley Tong, and starring Jackie Chan, Anita Mui, Françoise Yip, and Bill Tung. The film is about a Hong Kong police officer (Chan) who arrives in the Bronx area of New York City to meet his uncle and comes up against a local gang of street thugs.
